{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "27", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "22", "M": "19", "S": "44"}}, "news": [{"title": "Notandas Realty strengthens its legacy of craftsmanship with ultra-modern luxury innovation", "para": "Notandas Realty has carved a niche as a top-tier luxury developer within Mumbai\u2019s fast-paced real estate landscape. Boasting close to two decades of industry insight, the company specializes in stunning homes and high-end commercial areas. Guided by the visionary Mr. Harsh Jagwani, Notandas Realty leverages modern technology to ensure superior service and operational excellence.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/brand-connect-initiative/notandas-realty-strengthens-its-legacy-of-craftsmanship-with-ultra-modern-luxury-innovation/129844295?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-184560/129844295.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "brand-connect-initiative"}, {"title": "Birla Estates, Arvind SmartSpaces enter Mumbai\u2019s redevelopment segment with new housing projects", "para": "Birla Estates and Arvind SmartSpaces are expanding into Mumbai's property market. They have launched new redevelopment projects in Khar West and Santacruz. These ventures tap into the city's demand for housing. These projects represent significant revenue potential for both companies.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/birla-estates-arvind-smartspaces-enter-mumbais-redevelopment-segment-with-new-housing-projects/129844921?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-59802/129844921.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Madhuri Dixit leases commercial property in Mumbai for \u20b92.81 crore", "para": "Bollywood star Madhuri Dixit has leased a commercial space in Mumbai's One Lodha Place for a substantial monthly rent starting at \u20b94.25 lakh. The five-year agreement, registered in March 2026, includes a 67.91 sq meter unit and parking.  Rent escalates annually, culminating in a total lease value of \u20b92.81 crore over the term.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/madhuri-dixit-leases-prime-commercial-space-in-mumbai-for-281-crore/129844224?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-33784/129844224.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}]}